results.name: Number of covers of an unlabeled n-set such that every point of the set is covered by exactly 4 subsets of the cover and that intersection of every 4 subsets of the cover contains at most one point.
comment: Cover may include multiple occurrences of a subset. Also n-rowed binary matrices with distinct rows and all row sums 4.
results.author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Nov 30 2000
